title: Fighting Thru Jeanette Loff Ken Maynard

sources.title: Fighting Thru Jeanette Loff Ken Maynard
sources.description: Jeanette Loff, Ken Maynard, Wallace McDonald, and Carmelita Geraghty star in the 1930 western Fighting Thru. It was also known as California in 1878. There are some issues with the sound. ~ See more Jeanette Loff at http://www.jeanetteloff.com
